MPEG-7 SOUND CLASSIFICATION AND SIMILARITY TOOLS
Author: Michael A. Casey - Mitsubishi Electric Research Labs, Cambridge, USA
Date: 02/15/02
Version: 0.2 ALPHA (Works but is still being integrated)
Contact: Michael Casey: casey@merl.com

AudioSpectrumBasis.m -- computes AudioSpectrumBasisD and AudioSpectrumProjectionD from a spectrum.

Also see: SoundRecognitionModelDS:
SoundRecognitionTools.zip -- complete software package for using AudioSpectrumBasisD, AudioSpectrumProjectionD and ContinuousHiddenMarkovModelDS with SoundRecognitionModelDS and SoundClassificationModelDS. Currently being integrated for XM.

Expected Completion: 02/25/02

